<plot>An aspiring classical composer who writes radio jingles on the side becomes obsessed with plotting his own death as he draws closer to his 27th birthday. He believes himself to be another victim of the "Curse of the 27 Club" which causes musicians to die at the age of 27. Other victims of this curse have included Kurt Cobain, Janis Joplin, Jimi Hendrix and Jim Morrison among others.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?134621</url></doc>
